  - Discernment-Truth=Knowledge=The Excellence of Wisdom
By: Plato
---
Of the heaven which is above the heavens, what earthly poet ever did or ever
will sing worthily? ... There abides the very being with which true knowledge
is concerned; the colourless, formless, intangible essence ... knowledge
absolute in existence absolute.
